msgid "Subsurface Scattering"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/render/eevee/render_settings/subsurface_scattering.rst:7
msgid ""
"This effect mimics real subsurface scattering by blurring the diffuse lighting "
"in screen space."
msgstr ""
"Cet effet imite le *subsurface scattering* réel en floutant l'éclairage diffus "
"dans l'espace de scène."

